<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>예약 바우처 | 괌세이브카드</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .voucher-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        /* 헤더 */
        .voucher-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .voucher-header h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .voucher-header p {
            font-size: 12px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        /* 중요 공지 */
        .important-notice {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            margin: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .important-notice strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        /* 예약 정보 */
        .section {
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #495057;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .section-title::before {
            content: '';
            width: 4px;
            height: 16px;
            background: #667eea;
            margin-right: 8px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f3f5;
        }
        
        .info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            flex: 0 0 90px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            flex: 1;
            color: #212529;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        /* 컨펌번호 강조 */
        .confirmation-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px dashed #667eea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 15px;
        }
        
        .confirmation-box .label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .confirmation-box .number {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        
        /* QR 코드 */
        .qr-box {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        .qr-box img {
            max-width: 200px;
            height: auto;
            border: 2px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: white;
        }
        
        /* 이용방법 */
        .usage-guide {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 15px;
        }
        
        .usage-guide h3 {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #495057;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .usage-guide ol, .usage-guide ul {
            margin-left: 18px;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #495057;
        }
        
        .usage-guide li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        
        /* 주의사항 */
        .notice-list {
            padding: 15px;
        }
        
        .notice-list ul {
            list-style: none;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #6c757d;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .notice-list li {
            padding-left: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .notice-list li::before {
            content: '•';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        /* 연락처 */
        .contact-section {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .contact-section h3 {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .contact-section p {
            font-size: 12px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        .contact-section a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        /* 푸터 */
        .voucher-footer {
            background: #212529;
            color: #adb5bd;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 10px;
        }
        
        .voucher-footer p {
            margin: 3px 0;
        }
        
        /* 뱃지 */
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .badge-primary {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .badge-success {
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .badge-warning {
            background: #ffc107;
            color: #212529;
        }
        
        /* 인쇄 스타일 */
        @media print {
            body {
                background: white;
                padding: 0;
            }
            
            .voucher-container {
                box-shadow: none;
            }
        }
        
        /* 다크모드 대응 */
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body {
                background: #1a1a1a;
            }
            
            .voucher-container {
                background: #2d2d2d;
            }
            
            .section {
                border-bottom-color: #404040;
            }
            
            .info-value {
                color: #e9ecef;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="voucher-container">
        <!-- 헤더 -->
        <div class="voucher-header">
            <h1>🎫 예약 바우처</h1>
            <p>RESERVATION VOUCHER</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 중요 공지 -->
        <div class="important-notice">
            <strong>⚠️ 중요 안내</strong>
            이 바우처는 예약 확인증입니다. 이용 시 본 화면 또는 출력물을 반드시 제시해주세요.
        </div>
        
        <!-- 예약 기본 정보 -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">📋 예약 정보</div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <div class="info-label">예약번호</div>
                <div class="info-value"><%= reservation.reservation_number %></div>
            </div>
            <% if (reservation.platform_name) { %>
            <div class="info-row">
                <div class="info-label">예약 업체</div>
                <div class="info-value">
                    <span class="badge" style="background: #f0f4ff; color: #667eea; font-size: 12px; padding: 4px 10px;">
                        <%= reservation.platform_name %>
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% } %>
            <div class="info-row">
                <div class="info-label">예약자명</div>
                <div class="info-value">
                    <%= reservation.korean_name %> 
                    <% if (reservation.english_last_name || reservation.english_first_name) { %>
                        (<%= (reservation.english_last_name || '') %> <%= (reservation.english_first_name || '') %>)
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <div class="info-label">상품명</div>
                <div class="info-value"><strong><%= reservation.product_name %></strong></div>
            </div>
            <% if (reservation.package_type) { %>
            <div class="info-row">
                <div class="info-label">옵션</div>
                <div class="info-value"><%= reservation.package_type %></div>
            </div>
            <% } %>
            <div class="info-row">
                <div class="info-label">이용일자</div>
                <div class="info-value"><strong style="color: #667eea;"><%= formatDate(reservation.usage_date) %></strong></div>
            </div>
            <% if (reservation.usage_time) { %>
            <div class="info-row">
                <div class="info-label">이용시간</div>
                <div class="info-value"><%= reservation.usage_time %></div>
            </div>
            <% } %>
            <div class="info-row">
                <div class="info-label">인원</div>
                <div class="info-value">
                    성인 <%= reservation.people_adult || 0 %>명
                    <% if (reservation.people_child > 0) { %>, 아동 <%= reservation.people_child %>명<% } %>
                    <% if (reservation.people_infant > 0) { %>, 유아 <%= reservation.people_infant %>명<% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 컨펌번호 (있는 경우) -->
        <% if (confirmation_number) { %>
        <div class="confirmation-box">
            <div class="label">CONFIRMATION NUMBER</div>
            <div class="number"><%= confirmation_number %></div>
            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 8px;">
                이용 시 반드시 제시해주세요
            </p>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <!-- QR 코드 (있는 경우) -->
        <% if (qr_code_data || qr_image_path) { %>
        <div class="qr-box">
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; margin-bottom: 10px;">입장 QR 코드</p>
            <% if (qr_image_path) { %>
                <img src="/<%= qr_image_path %>" alt="QR Code" style="max-width: 300px; height: auto;">
            <% } else { %>
                <div id="qrcode"></div>
                <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/qrcode-generator@1.4.4/qrcode.min.js"></script>
                <script>
                    var qr = qrcode(0, 'M');
                    qr.addData('<%= qr_code_data %>');
                    qr.make();
                    document.getElementById('qrcode').innerHTML = qr.createImgTag(4);
                </script>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <!-- 업체 바우처 (있는 경우) -->
        <% if (vendor_voucher_path) { %>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">🎫 업체 발급 바우처</div>
            <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%); border-radius: 12px; border: 2px dashed #667eea;">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 48px;">
                    📄
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #495057; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 600;">
                    제공업체가 발급한 공식 바우처
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    이용 시 반드시 제시하거나 출력하여 지참해주세요
                </p>
                <a href="/api/vouchers/download/<%= vendor_voucher_path.split('/').pop() %>" 
                   download
                   style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 32px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4); transition: transform 0.2s;"
                   onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'"
                   onmouseout="this.style.transform='translateY(0)'">
                    📥 업체 바우처 다운로드
                </a>
                <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #868e96; margin-top: 12px;">
                    파일명: <%= vendor_voucher_path.split('/').pop() %>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <!-- AI 생성 이용방법 -->
        <% if (usage_instructions) { %>
        <div class="usage-guide">
            <h3>📍 이용 방법</h3>
            <%- usage_instructions %>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <!-- 수배업체 정보 -->
        <% if (vendor_name) { %>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">🏢 제공업체</div>
            <div class="info-row">
                <div class="info-label">업체명</div>
                <div class="info-value"><%= vendor_name %></div>
            </div>
            <% if (vendor_contact) { %>
            <div class="info-row">
                <div class="info-label">연락처</div>
                <div class="info-value"><a href="tel:<%= vendor_contact %>"><%= vendor_contact %></a></div>
            </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <!-- 주의사항 -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">⚠️ 주의사항</div>
            <div class="notice-list">
                <ul>
                    <li>예약 시간 최소 10분 전에 도착해주세요.</li>
                    <li>예약 변경은 이용일 1일 전까지 가능합니다.</li>
                    <li>노쇼(No-show) 시 취소 수수료가 발생할 수 있습니다.</li>
                    <li>기상 악화 등 불가피한 사유로 일정이 변경될 수 있습니다.</li>
                    <li>본인 확인을 위해 신분증을 지참해주세요.</li>
                    <% if (reservation.memo) { %>
                    <li style="color: #dc3545; font-weight: 600;">특이사항: <%= reservation.memo %></li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 고객센터 -->
        <div class="contact-section">
            <h3>💬 문의사항이 있으신가요?</h3>
            <p>고객센터: <a href="tel:+16717898989">+1 (671) 789-8989</a></p>
            <p>이메일: <a href="mailto:support@guamsavecard.com">support@guamsavecard.com</a></p>
            <p>카카오톡: @괌세이브카드</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 푸터 -->
        <div class="voucher-footer">
            <p><strong>GUAM SAVE CARD</strong></p>
            <p>발급일시: <%= new Date().toLocaleString('ko-KR', {timeZone: 'Pacific/Guam'}) %></p>
            <p>Voucher ID: <%= voucher_token.substring(0, 12).toUpperCase() %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
